From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|wagen||to pledge|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|xno|en}}, {{etyl|ONF.|en}} {{term|wagier|lang=fro}}, a northern variant of {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|guagier|lang=fro}} (whence modern French {{term|gager|lang=fr}}), itself either from {{term|guage|lang=fro}} or from a derivative of {{etyl|frk|en}} *''waddi'', *''wadja'', possibly through a {{etyl|VL.|en}} intermediate *''wadiare'' from *''wadium''.

